               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 1ra-58vb)
 I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 2ra-4rb)
 I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 4va-9vb)
 - On John the Evangelist as the author of the
                     book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 4va-8rb)
 - Story
                     of the family of Adam (fols. 8rb-9vb)
 I-3) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of
                     Jesus”: 29 miracles (fols. 1ra-1vb; 9vb-58vb) 
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
