                        <date>19th century.</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; the words mǝʿrāf,
                           nägär and täʾamr; incipit of Text I-1; the word ʾǝsaggǝd in Text I-1;
                           incipits of subsections of Texts I-2 and I-3; notes in the upper margins;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals; in the incipit page
                           of Text I-1 lines are rubricated, alternating with black lines (s. fol.
                           2r).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">Hand a: quires
