                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#45rb">f. 45rb</locus>
                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#45rb">45rb</locus>, <locus target="#18">18</locus>:
                              ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ መጽሐፍ[sic]፡ ዘአጽሐፍክዋ፡ አነ፡ ገብረ፡ ድንግል፡ ለቤተ፡ መስቀል፡ በወርቅየ[sic]፡
                              ከመ፡ ይኩነኒ፡ አስበ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት። ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዞ፡ ለይኩን፡ በአፈ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡
                              ወጳውሎስ፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#45r">45r</locus>: I had this book written, Gabra
                              Dǝngǝl, for the Beta Masqal of Warqǝya, so that it might be for me a
                              reward in the Heavenly Kingdom. Anyone who stole it or erased (its)
                              text, be excommunicated through the mouth of Peter and Paul. </quote>
                           <note> </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">Readings are indicated by the names of the feasts
