                                 22r</locus> - በጥምቅት: <locus target="#25r">fol. 25r</locus> - በቃና፡
                              ዘገሊላ: <locus target="#27v">fol. 27v</locus> - በእኁድ: <locus target="#29r">fol. 29r</locus> - በሆሣዕና: <locus target="#31v">fol.
                                 31v</locus> - በጸሎተ፡ ሐሙስ: <locus target="#34v">fol. 34v</locus> -
                              በዓርብ፡ <locus target="#35v">fol. 35v</locus> - Unreadable, the edge was
                              trimmed: <locus target="#37v">fol. 37v</locus> - በትንሣኤ: <locus target="#39v">fol. 39v</locus> - በዕርገት፡ ወበዓለ፡ ፶: <locus target="#43v">fol. 43v</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
